issue.title: Use the header and footers from mol.org
issue.body: Looks like we're still using local header and footer here.

issue.title: New groups
issue.body:
I've updated the route `/indicators/completeness` to take a taxa argument:

https://api.mol.org/0.x/indicators/completeness?indicator=gbif&taxa=amphibians

https://api.mol.org/0.x/indicators/completeness?indicator=gbif&taxa=dragonflies
